text: Parahepomidion granulipenne is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1955.BioLib.cz - Parahepomidion granulipenne. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1955
